OL,3,CPope Francis would have felt 'at home'
OL,4,Cin North West
OL,6,FArchbishop of Liverpool, the Most
OL,7,FReverend Malcolm McMahon, pays tribute
OL,8,Fto the Pope and says he would have
OL,9,Fresonated with those in the North West
OL,11,FPope Francis shared the same sense of
OL,12,Fhumour and warmth as those living in
OL,13,Fthe North West and would have "felt at
OL,14,Fhome" here, the Archbishop of
OL,15,FLiverpool has said in tribute.
OL,17,FThe head of the Catholic church died
OL,18,Faged 88 on Easter Monday following
OL,19,Fweeks of health issues, the Vatican
OL,20,Fconfirmed.
