OL,3,CPope Francis would have felt 'at home'
OL,4,Cin North West
OL,6,F"He was a very happy, warm man. He had
OL,7,Fa deep kind of joy really within him.
OL,8,FI think it came from that thing that
OL,9,Fwe're all seeking, which is an inner
OL,10,Fpeace."
OL,12,FSpeaking of the North West and in
OL,13,Fparticular Liverpool, he added: "I
OL,14,Fthink the Holy Father would feel at
OL,15,Fhome here because he had a great sense
OL,16,Fof humour just like the like
OL,17,FLiverpudlians.
