OL,6,FThe Right Reverend John Arnold, Bishop
OL,7,Fof Salford, paid tribute to the Pope
OL,8,Fwho 'always had a smile and humour'
OL,10,FThe Right Reverend John Arnold, Bishop
OL,11,Fof Salford, also paid tribute to Pope
OL,12,FFrancis, saying he showed "such
OL,13,Fdetermination to fulfil his
OL,14,Fcommitments and return to his
OL,15,Fministry" despite his illnesses.
OL,17,F"There was always the smile, the warm
OL,18,Fhandshake, always wanting to know what
OL,19,Fwe wanted to say when we went as
OL,20,Fgroups, and always with humour too,
OL,21,Fand it was lovely," he said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/14
