OL,6,F"I hope that that will initiate some
OL,7,Fradical changes in the way we live,
OL,8,Fparticularly in the way we deal with
OL,9,Fthe environment and climate change,
OL,10,Fbut particularly also among people who
OL,11,Freally do not have a decent standard
OL,12,Fof life and living, while the rich get
OL,13,Frich and so many of the poor just get
OL,14,Fpoorer, that's not a just world."
OL,16,FBooks of condolences have been opened
OL,17,Facross the region, including at
OL,18,FLiverpool Metropolitan Cathedral.
