OL,6,FOne man, who had just signed the book,
OL,7,Fsaid: "I think it's a very sad day for
OL,8,Fthe catholic church.
OL,10,F"Even though Pope Francis had been ill
OL,11,Ffor quite sometime, it's still a great
OL,12,Fshock when somebody dies, we will all
OL,13,Ffeel sad at the loss of a very lovely
OL,14,Fman."
OL,16,FAnother woman, who said she was not
OL,17,Freligious, said she felt compelled to
OL,18,Fcome after hearing the news.
