OL,6,F"When somebody told me the Pope had
OL,7,Fpassed away it felt like a historic
OL,8,Fday and it's important to me to
OL,9,Facknowledge his passing as a human
OL,10,Fbeing who was doing good in the world,
OL,11,Fso I can and I signed the book of
OL,12,Fcondolence," she said.
OL,14,FIn 2023 the Bishop, alongside the Dean
OL,15,Fof Manchester and Greater Manchester
OL,16,FMayor Andy Burnham visited the Vatican
OL,17,Fto meet with the Pope to discuss
OL,18,Fclimate change.
